### Beads / Dolt
# Per-clone bd state (Dolt working copy, lockfiles, runtime artifacts,
# per-machine metadata.json) is excluded by .beads/.gitignore (tracked
# itself, once the tenant is provisioned). `.beads/config.yaml` IS tracked:
# it carries the server-mode connection block for the livespec-driver-codex
# Dolt tenant with NO per-machine project_id and NO password (the tenant
# password is supplied via the BEADS_DOLT_PASSWORD env var at bd-call time).
# The beads tenant is DEFERRED to a later family-infra phase (see
# .livespec.jsonc), so no `.beads/` tree exists yet.
.beads-credential-key
*.env.local
